phase.description:
The current phase of PersistentVolumeClaim.

- `"Bound"`: The PVC is already bound;
- `"Pending"`: The PVC is not yet bound;
- `"Lost"`: The PVC has lost its underlying PersistentVolume. The claim was bound to a PersistentVolume and the volume does not exist any longer and all data on it was lost.
